A Small Watchdog Daemon                                           -*-README-*-

This is the watchdogd from uClinux-dist, originally by Michele d'Amico and
later adapted to uClinux-dist by Mike Frysinger.

	http://www.mail-archive.com/uclinux-dev@uclinux.org/msg04191.html

The original code has no license and is available from:

	http://www.uclinux.org/pub/uClinux/dist/

Below is the email conversation about the licensing.  You can use this if
you want to redistribute the original as public domain.

